Module nl.naturalis.common
Package nl.naturalis.common.collection

Class TypeGraphSet

java.lang.Object
nl.naturalis.common.collection.TypeGraphSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<Class<?>>, Collection<Class<?>>, Set<Class<?>>
public class TypeGraphSet extends Object
A specialized Set implementation for Class objects. It returns true from its contains method if the set contains the specified type or any of its super types.
See Also:
